      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·豳風·002.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">鴟鴞.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>鴟鴞鴟鴞，既取我子，無毀我室！恩斯勤斯，鬻子之閔斯。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>O owl, O owl,
You have taken my young ones; —
Do not [also] destroy my nest.
With love and with toil
I nourished them. — I am to
be pitied.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-binfeng-002__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
