      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·豳風·002.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">鴟鴞.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>迨天之未陰雨，徹彼桑土。綢繆牖戶。今女下民，或敢侮予。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Before the sky was dark with rain,
I gathered the roots of the mulberry tree,
And bound round and round my window and door.
Now ye people below,
Dare any of you despise my house?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-binfeng-002__003__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
