      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·豳風·002.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">鴟鴞.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>予手拮据，予所捋荼。予所蓄租，予口卒瘏。曰予未有室家。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>With my claws I tore and held.
Through the rushes which I gathered,
And all the materials I collected,
My mouth was all sore; —
I said to myself, 'I have not yet got my house complete.'</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-binfeng-002__004__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
