      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·豳風·002.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">鴟鴞.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>予羽譙譙，予尾翛翛。予室翹翹，風雨所漂搖。予維音嘵嘵。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>My wings are all-injured;
My tail is all-broken;
My house is in a perilous condition;
It is tossed about in the wind and rain: —
I can but cry out with this note of alarm.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
